description: If it's power you need, then with the Innergie mCube mini, it is power you'll get. The ultra-compact design is stylish and powerful with a 90 watt output, compatible with over 15 leading brands of laptops and over 10,000 portable devices. In addition to the 90 watt power capability, there is also a 10 watt USB port for charging your iPad or other media devices. Ships with 10 connectors for different manufacturers and charger is energy efficient with multiple built-in protections.
title: Innergie mCube Mini 90 Watt Auto/Air Power Adapter and 10W USB Output (TADP-90AB AA) - White
